{"tid":1157252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華富邨男戶主食煙燒梳化險焚宅","createTime":"2019-05-16T06:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T08:26:05.000Z","uid":3090,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"39748fbaaa80d11f6089c308fb3aaf383077743b","tid":1157252,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T06:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dVh3dsv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdVh3dsv.png&h=f0f6a0be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/16/145336_403edfa050d4f0bf9f821707aceb38d7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F16%2F145336_403edfa050d4f0bf9f821707aceb38d7.png&h=11c835f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/16/145337_59f74e1600e1a9e2c1b58eeb27573467.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F16%2F145337_59f74e1600e1a9e2c1b58eeb27573467.png&h=402ca02d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港仔華富邨華裕樓，早上11時18分，其中一單位起火冒出濃煙，消防接報到場，出動一喉一煙帽隊，約半小時將火救熄。火警期間，約10多名住客自行疏散到地面，事件中無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n起火為三樓一個單位，男戶主當時在家中裝修，接近完成，其間他在吸煙，卻不慎打翻火酒，燃起梳化着火，冒出濃煙，驚動鄰居協助他一起救火。他事後赤腳逃生，並無受傷，「我同鄰居救熄咗㗎唰，不過好大煙！」現場瀰漫大陣燶味。消防經調查後，火警無可疑"},{"pid":"b1a6e49d3af2849adbe7b0f46f82c5c0e6158ae0","tid":1157252,"uid":49197,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T06:54:19.000Z","msg":"公屋+1分"},{"pid":"848398bf3c663fef8bd8d2585bf7d52a29c5c629","tid":1157252,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T06:55:13.000Z","msg":"永續裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54fc0ef1b74c5e6cb935ef14d0c4ec4fa1ee75f","tid":1157252,"uid":35870,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T06:55:17.000Z","msg":"煙撚害自己就算啦<br />\n累人累物<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0730258ef41206e6